description:
"We are witnessing a mass extinction event of young men"

Please join me in welcoming for the third time, Dr. K (Dr. Alok Kanojia), addiction expert, and a Harvard-trained psychiatrist to The Diary Of A CEO.

Known to millions through his work on Twitch (a.k.a HealthyGamerGG), Dr K is transforming the way we talk about addiction, loneliness, and the struggles facing young people today.

I’ve had countless conversations about addiction, but this one is different. 

He believes we're currently experiencing a silent crisis, a mass extinction event of young men who will never form relationships, families, or truly thrive in society.

We cover:

- Why porn addiction has become a global epidemic.
- Exactly what pornography does to your brain and why it’s hard to stop.
- The hidden cause behind all addictions nobody talks about.
- Why young men and women are drifting apart more than ever.
- The real reason so many men today feel lost and resentful.

This conversation gave a different lens to view mental health and addiction, one that doesn’t just focus on the individual, but also on society's role in creating these problems.

If you're struggling with loneliness, addiction, or simply feel trapped by your own mind, this is one you don’t want to miss.

Watch the full episode now on YouTube: search “The Diary of a CEO Dr K”
fulltitle: Masturbation Reprograms Your Brain Like A Drug!
